<p>Another method to view your friend posts and subscriptions is the &#8220;Friends Page,&#8221; a timeline of friend posts and subscriptions. You can therefore scroll down the list of your friend&#8217;s posts and subcriptions, just as you see it people doing it all the time on Facebook.</p>



